{"word":"ἀνάλυσις","slug":"ἀνάλυσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάλυσις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀναλύω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a loosing, releasing</i>, <el>κακῶν</el> <i>from</i> evils, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>) <i>retirement, departure, death</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}